    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In SCRAPS BATTLE, travel through time and space and face off against your friends in wacky challenges ! As a 4-man team, travel through the ages and complete mini-games to try to win the title of SCRAPS KING.<strong> </strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >UP TO 4 PLAYER WITH CHANGEABLE TEAMS !<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211020/extras/e8337a8847332b70ab8bff9a57c6007e.poster.avif?t=1770224190\" width=800 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211020/extras/e8337a8847332b70ab8bff9a57c6007e.webm?t=1770224190\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211020/extras/e8337a8847332b70ab8bff9a57c6007e.mp4?t=1770224190\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play with 3 friends and compete in a sequence of mini-games with constantly shifting teams. Either in 1 versus all, 2 against 2 or in a free for all, never loose sight of your one and only objective, fight for victory ! <br> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >DIFFERENT TIME PERIODS !<br>  </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Beware, because the Time-Machine is up to no good! From Pirates to robots from the future, travel through time to collect key artifacts necessary to ensure your victory.<br> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >BE THE ROBOT OF THE MONTH.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211020/extras/f2bb881baf3cf2d8a7d39557163d9932.poster.avif?t=1770224190\" width=800 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211020/extras/f2bb881baf3cf2d8a7d39557163d9932.webm?t=1770224190\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211020/extras/f2bb881baf3cf2d8a7d39557163d9932.mp4?t=1770224190\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play a succesion of mini-games with your friends in the gamemode SCRAPS KING, and try to become the first one to win 5 artifacts to be awarded the title of ROBOT OF THE MONTH by the &quot;inventor&quot; !</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ENDLESS REPLAYABILITY !<br> </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The free selection mode gives you the ability to play any mini-games of your choice freely with no limit !</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A GAMEBREAKING PHYSICS !<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211020/extras/e8fb7e90393bf0e356a9487655dfc223.poster.avif?t=1770224190\" width=800 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211020/extras/e8fb7e90393bf0e356a9487655dfc223.webm?t=1770224190\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211020/extras/e8fb7e90393bf0e356a9487655dfc223.mp4?t=1770224190\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>     </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take control of the robot of your choice and get ready to have some fun and use the ever-present physics to create wild outcomes !</p>",
